nd Thursday, too=E2=80=A6).<br/><br/>There=E2=80=99s a lot going on in the =
art world as we enter the final two weeks before the November auction in Ne=
w York. Phillips, Christie=E2=80=99s, and Sotheby=E2=80=99s have all put th=
eir auction catalogs online, so we now know what=E2=80=99s on offer. It wil=
l take a little time to digest, but I=E2=80=99ll have an overview sometime =
next week. <br/><br/>Today, I=E2=80=99m looking at collector <b>Larry Warsh=
