there=E2=80=99s no playbook for that. But MoMA also needs someone who no lo=
nger has the drive to <i>build</i>. It=E2=80=99s hard to imagine an ambitio=
us museum director in their early 40s choosing the staid MoMA job over the =
opportunity in
Dallas.</li></ul>
