=99s closes on the Breuer building=E2=80=A6 and opens a new set of question=
s</i>: Suddenly, all the talk and speculation about Sotheby=E2=80=99s is le=
ss about its billion-dollar cash infusion and more about real estate. On Mo=
nday, the auction house announced, via <i>The New York Times</i>, that it <=
u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2Uk=
