m5hbCI6ImY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZDEyYSIsImxpbmtfaWQiOjE5NjU5MTB9/df5642a6ec458ec=
5f32b65cb172a06e2d8a704db8a108fef3abcb159c44a973c" style=3D"color:#d40000;t=
ext-decoration:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">sold by Sotheby=E2=80=
=99s</a></u> and has been consigned by <b>Allan Schwartzman</b>. Althoff wa=
s represented by the gallery of <b>Barbara</b> <b>Gladstone</b>, who was fi=
ercely protective of her artists, and who died unexpectedly at the age of 8=
